'''阴茎击剑'''（{{lang-en|Penis fencing}}）是某些种类的[[扁形动物|扁虫]]的交配方式。

==描述==
一些[[雌雄同体|雌雄同体]]的扁虫（例如Pseudobiceros属的扁虫）采取这种交配方式。这些扁虫同时拥有[[精巢|精巢]]和[[卵巢|卵巢]]，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pbs.org/kcet/shapeoflife/episodes/hunt_explo2.html |title=Fighting to mate: flatworm penis fencing |author=Leslie Newman |publisher=[[Public_Broadcasting_Service|PBS]] |accessdate=2015-03-11 |archive-date=2013-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131114002014/http://www.pbs.org/kcet/shapeoflife/episodes/hunt_explo2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>并长有两只白色，短剑状的[[阴茎|阴茎]]。在交配中，两虫相对而斗。每只扁虫都试图首先将自己的阴茎刺入对方皮下并释放精子。<ref name="Michiels">Michiels, N.K., and L.J. Newman. (1998). Sex and violence in hermaphrodites. ''Nature'' 391:647.</ref><ref name="sn">[http://www.sciencenews.org/pages/sn_arc98/2_14_98/fob2.htm Hermaphrodites duel for manhood] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencenews.org/pages/sn_arc98/2_14_98/fob2.htm |date=20080326155753 }}, ''Science News Online''. Accessed 14 March 2009.</ref><ref name="theawk">{{cite video|people=Sonne, L., [[Peter_Coyote|Coyote, P.]], [[Leslie_Newman|Newman, L.]]|date=2001|title=The shape of life|url=http://www.pbs.org/kcet/shapeoflife/video/tv_high.html?ep_hunt_explo2_mov_hi|format=rm|publisher=[[Public_Broadcasting_Station|PBS]]|accessdate=15 February 2010|medium=Television production|archive-date=2012-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026100439/http://www.pbs.org/kcet/shapeoflife/video/tv_high.html?ep_hunt_explo2_mov_hi|dead-url=no}}</ref> 这一过程通常持续一个小时。<ref name=NatGeo>{{cite web|title=World's Weirdest: Flatworm Penis Fencing|url=http://video.nationalgeographic.com/video/weirdest-flatworms|website=National Geographic|accessdate=14 June 2014|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402112639/http://video.nationalgeographic.com/video/weirdest-flatworms|dead-url=no}}</ref>战斗结束后，败者将接受胜者的[[精子|精子]]，成为“母亲”。

就生物学角度而言，培育后代是一项费时费力的工作。所以依据Bateman原理，做“父亲”比做“母亲”更为有利。因而一些雌雄同体的生物采取这样一种方式交配。<ref name="sn" />

